extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Music Hub], a very basic Express API created by Dan Hayworth.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Song:] !{data.song_count}
      li #[strong Artists:] !{data.artist_count}
      li #[strong Albums:] !{data.album_count}
